data.description: Move-in Ready! Discover refined living in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, showcasing an elegant and spacious study with French doors.  The spacious living room bathes in natural light, complemented by a well-appointed kitchen featuring modern appliances. Retreat to the master suite or utilize two additional bedrooms, perfect for guests or a growing family.  The privacy fenced backyard provides a private space, and the attached garage adds practicality. With updated luxury vinyl flooring and proximity to schools, parks, and amenities, this home seamlessly blends style and comfort. Schedule a showing today!
